RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

96-2328. State ex rel. Guess v. Clerks, Common Pleas Court.

Franklin App. No. 96APD05-660. Reported at 77 Ohio St.3d 1464, 672 N.E.2d 1121. IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration in this case be, and hereby is, denied, effective December 17,1996.
